data.title: Classic Tiramisù Recipe (with Video) - NYT Cooking
data.description: Done correctly, a classic tiramisù can be transcendent A creamy dessert of espresso-soaked ladyfingers surrounded by lightly sweetened whipped cream and a rich mascarpone, tiramisù relies heavily on the quality of its ingredients If you don’t have a barista setup at home, pick up the espresso at a local coffee shop, or use strongly brewed coffee
